Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:57.52,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H5354EC&\blur10\bord2\fad(100,200)}你们是食物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:59.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H5354EC&\blur10\bord2\fad(100,200)}不，我们是猎人！
